videos.description: Tremont Waters flings a lob to Marlon Taylor who puts home the alley-oop.
videos.headline: Taylor flies in to dunk home lob

videos.description: Kentucky's PJ Washington feels the double team and dishes to a wide-open Reid Travis for the slam.
videos.headline: Washington's sweet pass leads to powerful slam

videos.description: Kentucky breaks LSU's press and only needs one dribble before a Reid Travis alley-oop.
videos.headline: Kentucky needs only one dribble to get downcourt for easy bucket

videos.description: Emmitt Williams grabs the long pass, pump fakes and finishes the easy layup.
videos.headline: Williams' nice pump fake sets up easy bucket for LSU

videos.description: Tremont Waters puts in a tough reverse layup.
videos.headline: LSU's Waters scores circus layup.

videos.description: Kavell Bigby-Williams tips in a shot right before the horn sounds to lift LSU past Kentucky.
